text: Alexandria... Why? (, translit. Iskanderija... lih?) is a 1979 Egyptian drama movie directed by Youssef Chahine and starring Naglaa Fathi, Ahmed Zaki, Farid Shawqi, Mahmoud El-Meliguy, Ezzat El Alaili, Youssef Wahbi. == Other websites == * Category:1979 drama movies Category:1979 LGBT movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Youssef Chahine Category:Movies set in Egypt
title: Alexandria... Why?
